-- Shares of Pilgrim's Pride leap after waiver extension
-- 
-- Wed Nov 26, 2008 1:31pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/11/26/us-pilgrimspride-shares-idUSTRE4AP6TN20081126

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Pilgrim's Pride Corp PPC.N surged on Wednesday after the company said it had reached an agreement with lenders to extend its temporary covenant waiver for a third time. 

 Shares of the poultry producer were up 101.9 percent at $1.09 after earlier spiking as much as 174 percent. (Reporting by  Leah Schnurr ; Editing by Tom Hals)